      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">易經 49 初九</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">易經 49 初九</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>初九：鞏用黃牛之革。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>The first NINE, undivided, shows its subject (as if he were) bound with the skin of a yellow ox.</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
