      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">易經 49 六二</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">易經 49 六二</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>六二：己日乃革之，征吉，无咎。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>The second SIX, divided, shows its subject making his changes after some time has passed. Action taken will be fortunate. There will be no error.</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
