      <prop type="x-target-segment-count">1</prop>
      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">易經 49 九三</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">易經 49 九三</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>九三：征凶，貞厲，革言三就，有孚。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>The third NINE, undivided, shows that action taken by its subject will be evil. Though he be firm and correct, his position is perilous. If the change (he contemplates) have been three times fully discussed, he will be believed in.</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
