      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">易經 49 九四</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">易經 49 九四</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>九四：悔亡，有孚改命，吉。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>The fourth NINE, undivided, shows occasion for repentance disappearing (from its subject). Let him be believed in; and though he change (existing) ordinances, there will be good fortune.</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
