      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">易經 49 九五</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">易經 49 九五</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>九五：大人虎變，未占有孚。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>The fifth NINE, undivided, shows the great man (producing his changes) as the tiger (does when he) changes (his stripes). Before he divines (and proceeds to action), faith has been reposed in him.</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
