      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">易經 49 上六</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">易經 49 上六</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>上六：君子豹變，小人革面，征凶，居貞吉。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>The sixth SIX, divided, shows the superior man producing his changes as the leopard (does when he) changes (his spots), while small men change their faces (and show their obedience). To go forward (now) would lead to evil, but there will be good fortune in abiding firm and correct.</seg>
      </tuv>
